        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-314188206" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-314188206" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="314188206">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/elaine7599/">羊城咏儿</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2010-11-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">不知道可信与否。连拼音都和买的《诗经》全本不同。不过列了些参考著作，还是有学习价值的。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
